<rss version="2.0" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" xmlns:ss="http://contenthub.aol.com/slideshow/"><channel><title><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></title><link/> https://www.engadget.com/ <description><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></description><language> en-US</language><copyright>版权所有雅虎 2023</copyright><pubDate> Thu, 10 Aug 2023 16:00:01 +0000</pubDate><generator>雅虎 http://yahoo.com </generator><item><title><![CDATA[YouTube is deactivating links in Shorts videos to combat spam]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> YouTube 知道自己存在垃圾邮件问题，尤其是推出<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/youtube-shorts-available-globally-161554248.html">两年前的 Shorts 功能</a>。为了对此采取措施，该流媒体宣布将停用 Shorts 描述、评论和垂直直播中的链接。 YouTube 还取消了点击任何桌面频道横幅上的社交媒体图标的功能。新的变化将于 8 月 31 日开始推出。</p><p>尽管 YouTube 声称不会继续其“不可点击”的讨伐，但它补充道，“由于滥用策略发展迅速，我们必须采取预防措施，让诈骗者和垃圾邮件发送者更难通过链接误导或欺骗用户。”与此同时，YouTube 正在创作者频道上添加新链接，从 8 月 23 日开始，订阅按钮旁将出现一个可点击的大链接。该链接可以将用户带到从商品网站到社交媒体帐户的任何内容。该平台最近还推出了<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/youtube-is-adding-more-creator-tools-to-shorts-to-help-it-take-on-tiktok-160023789.html">更多 Shorts 创作者工具</a>，例如画外音。不过，至少要到 9 月底，该流媒体才会推出“更安全”的方式来引导人们从 Shorts 短视频返回到其他内容。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/ebf97e20-3772-11ee-a77f-07eedf1cd536" style="height:1000px;width:1100px;" alt="两张移动图像显示了 Shorts 视频上的链接位置。" data-uuid="bbbb2126-da65-3a23-ae25-f059c37932a1"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> YouTube</div></figure><p>据报道，除了链接之外，YouTube 还致力于减少<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/youtube-comment-spam-channel-impersonators-150007960.html">假冒帐户</a>的数量，方法是改进用于查找这些帐户并随后将其删除的策略。据该平台称，与 2022 年第一季度相比，2023 年第一季度因冒充而被删除的账户数量增加了 35% 以上（不过尚不清楚这是因为更好的政策还是只是因为更多的虚假账户）。该流媒体还通过其最近的“增加严格度”功能保留了更多评论以供审核。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/youtube-is-deactivating-links-in-shorts-videos-to-combat-spam-160001356.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/youtube-is-deactivating-links-in-shorts-videos-to-combat-spam-160001356.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 46efe953-59e8-461d-a59a-8854e9634593</guid><dc:creator>萨拉·菲尔丁</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Thu, 10 Aug 2023 16:00:01 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691668526</ingested><modified> 2023-08-10T11:55:37+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Sarah Fielding]]></category><media:content height="4600" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-05/f2e80bc0-f42e-11ed-ae3a-1219dd476360" width="6897"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="4600" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-05/f2e80bc0-f42e-11ed-ae3a-1219dd476360" width="6897"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[NurPhoto via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[YouTube logo is displayed on a mobile phone screen for illustration photo. Krakow, Poland on February 9, 2023.  (Photo by Beata Zawrzel/NurPhoto via Getty Images)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Big Tech Logos]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The Television Academy has delayed the Emmys until January]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/disney-bringing-andor-to-tv-and-hulu-193448433.html"><em><ins>《安道尔》</ins></em></a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-last-of-us-finale-sums-up-everything-the-shows-first-season-did-right-134544926.html"><em><ins>《最后生还者》</ins></em></a>等电视剧的粉丝们，如果想知道自己喜欢的节目能否赢得<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/emmys/"><ins>艾美奖</ins></a>，就必须再耐心等待几个月。电视学院和福克斯<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.emmys.com/news/awards-news/emmys-230810">宣布</a>黄金时段艾美奖颁奖典礼将于 1 月 15 日（马丁·路德·金纪念日）举行，而不是 9 月 18 日。</p><p>这标志着推迟了四个月，这意味着颁奖典礼将在金球奖颁奖典礼一周后播出。电视学院及其广播合作伙伴也将创意艺术艾美奖推迟到了金球奖颁奖典礼的同一个周末（为期两晚的颁奖典礼的剪辑版本将于 1 月 13 日播出）。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>延迟并不意外。 <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-emmys-are-reportedly-delayed-due-to-ongoing-strikes-164958589.html"><ins>数周来一直有传言</ins></a>称，由于编剧和演员罢工导致好莱坞制作陷入停顿，学院和福克斯将不得不推迟艾美奖颁奖典礼。由于没有美国作家协会成员可以为艾美奖主持人写笑话，而美国演员工会联合会（SAG-AFTRA）的演员也因工会关于推广罢工作品的规定而无法参加颁奖典礼，因此重新安排时间似乎是不可避免的。</p><p>演员和作家举行罢工，试图与好莱坞电影公司签订公平的合同，以保护他们职业的未来。主要争论点之一是，两个工会都希望<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/hollywood-writers-demand-protections-against-ai-exploitation-143007545.html"><ins>保护其成员</ins></a>免受可能损害其就业前景的人工智能进步的影响。例如，SAG-AFTRA 声称制片厂希望扫描演员，并有权<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/striking-actors-say-rejected-ai-proposal-would-let-studios-use-their-likeness-without-fair-pay-000025878.html"><ins>永久使用他们的数字肖像</ins></a>，以换取一天的报酬。</p><p>正如几年来的情况一样，流媒体服务的节目和电视电影正在与广播网络的节目和电视电影争夺艾美奖的荣耀。凭借<em>《最后生还者》</em>和《继承之<em>战》</em>等影片，HBO 和 Max 总共<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/hbos-the-last-of-us-adaptation-scoops-up-24-emmy-nominations-171117148.html"><ins>获得了</ins></a>127 项提名。 Netflix 获得了 103 项提名，Apple（在艾美奖卫冕冠军泰德·拉索<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/ted-lasso-season-three-preview-080056592.html"><em><ins>(Ted Lasso</ins></em></a> ) 的大力帮助下）获得了 52 项提名。Disney+ 今年获得了 40 项艾美奖提名，这在很大程度上要归功于其多部<a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/star-wars/"><ins>《星球大战》</ins></a>剧集。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/the-television-academy-has-delayed-the-emmys-until-january-144508081.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-television-academy-has-delayed-the-emmys-until-january-144508081.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> a5d61cc0-d8f7-4d05-a264-b92c3c3ae096</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Thu, 10 Aug 2023 14:45:08 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691677874</ingested><modified> 2023-08-10T14:31:19+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[Television]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="4000" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/ad759bf0-3788-11ee-bffd-03e20914ae56" width="6000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="4000" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/ad759bf0-3788-11ee-bffd-03e20914ae56" width="6000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]><